{"tid":1288084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]科大捐十萬比立場新聞","createTime":"2019-07-05T12:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T17:45:24.000Z","uid":135807,"like":241,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"42cf2fa79a7a605ae26431cbea07a6a9a4a70aac","tid":1288084,"uid":135807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:56:42.000Z","msg":"本校前校監梁振英先生以官司為名，打壓異己為實，連月來狙擊多間傳媒，加上反送中抗爭時警方多次暴力對待傳媒，讓本會擔憂香港之新聞自由是否名存實亡，故決議從反送中基金捐贈十萬港元予立場新聞，守衛香港核心價值，亦呼籲各界人士慷慨解囊，助傳媒渡過難關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKUSTSUCouncil/posts/2284182898355545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKUSTSUCouncil%2Fposts%2F2284182898355545&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=4037057b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKUSTSUCouncil/posts/2284182898355545</a>"},{"pid":"dd2fdaa8ade1fb81cfcb94575697b8a17d3c611c","tid":1288084,"uid":94771,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b072aba4d2acc06e7383339054d53a52223e4838","tid":1288084,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:57:48.000Z","msg":"反中大團結"},{"pid":"eb45a9dfee0ad06817830e1ff062f541a07f5549","tid":1288084,"uid":1544,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"科大今期出盡晒力"},{"pid":"65fee5f7e7f9ea3460f5447463e37c5ea02327da","tid":1288084,"uid":1544,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb45a9dfee0ad06817830e1ff062f541a07f5549","tid":1288084,"uid":1544,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"科大今期出盡晒力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:58:55.000Z","msg":"會唔會比人秋後算帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d913649d60f3293f30966c386b5021319d131f","tid":1288084,"uid":95452,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"真一大<img src=\"/assets/fac